translation:
Thus (speaks) the king of the land of Beirut: to the prefect of the land of Ugarit, my son, speak;
Hello to you!  May the gods keep you in a good state!
My son, here is my messenger, to execute my wishes, on the spot, in your country, I have sent him.  You, my son, look at him with a good eye!

